# Obligation (boolean safety + guarantee)
# from tests/survey_formulas.py (the curated survey corpus), AP-renamed to canonical a,b,c… -- resync via tests/benchmark/from_survey.py

Fa | Gb  # obligation: reachability OR invariant
Ga | Gb  # disjunction of invariants
Fa & Gb  # reach while maintaining an invariant
(a U b) | Gc  # until OR invariant
Ga | Fb  # the mixed safety/guarantee obligation
